544
00:42:35,350 --> 00:42:37,020
Hello.

545
00:42:37,020 --> 00:42:41,890
Luoxi, look how pretty Xiaofeng's friend is.

546
00:42:43,170 --> 00:42:46,830
Miss Mi Luo, I've already heard Xiaofeng speak of you. She said that you are her best friend.

547
00:42:46,830 --> 00:42:51,000
Now that I've met you, you really are generous, hearty, and charming.

548
00:42:51,000 --> 00:42:54,160
It's the first time a girl has praised me like that.

549
00:42:54,160 --> 00:42:57,500
Come! Let me introduce the wine I have here.

550
00:42:57,500 --> 00:42:59,140
All right, let's go.

551
00:42:59,140 --> 00:43:03,200
Here, look. This is my private collection.

552
00:43:03,200 --> 00:43:05,480
Men like stronger wine.

553
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:10,200
But for girls, you should choose a more fruity flavor so it will be easier to drink.

554
00:43:10,200 --> 00:43:14,500
Look. I have Tusu wine, Autumn Dew spirits, Misty Mellow wine,

555
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:20,400
Full Water Spring wine, Lotus Bud wine, Cold Sandalwood, Thousand Mile wine, Apricot wine, Golden Sand,

556
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:24,960
