557
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:28,020
Pear Blossom Spring wine, and Ruoxiachun wine.

558
00:43:29,350 --> 00:43:33,100
The names of these wines sound really nice. I've never heard of so many before.

559
00:43:33,100 --> 00:43:36,600
What types of wine do you usually like to drink?

560
00:43:36,600 --> 00:43:38,550
I have never drunk before.

561
00:43:38,550 --> 00:43:42,040
No way! You never drank wine?

562
00:43:42,700 --> 00:43:46,660
Then, for your birthday, we will drink our hearts out. Let's go.

